### Unenroll a Supabase MFA Factor Using JavaScript

Source: https://github.com/supabase/supabase/blob/master/apps/docs/content/guides/auth/auth-mfa.mdx

Demonstrates how to unenroll a Multi-Factor Authentication (MFA) factor using the Supabase JavaScript client. This requires an initialized Supabase client and the `factorId` of the specific MFA factor to be unenrolled. The `supabase.auth.mfa.unenroll()` method sends the request, removing the factor from the user's account.

